ss="value">Born in Cabilis West, I reached the age of rebirth and was honored to chosen to learn and excell in the arts of monkhood. 

After spending seven seasons performing tasks for my teachers I was taken into a band of monks known as "Fists of Fear." They however had internal conflict which brought their organization to it's knees. The following day after joining I had the pleasure of assisting a few monks from this guild to build a new one "The Scaled Brotherhood" which appeared to be as good as first. 

After spending another 44 seasons with this guild I completed all of the tasks that my teachers could find for one of my skill. 

Alas, this guild did not offer much to those who achieved higher enlightenment and as most of the others in my skill range left to further hone their skills, I too had to sadly depart.

I had thus joined Tolkien's Revenge and it would have apearred that I had much to learn from this new family. However, that family eventually turned it's back on me. I have joined Altruistic Volarians. And this family is the one I should have joined from the get go. I'll see what we can teach each other.</span></div>	</div> 	<div id="contactinfo">		<h2>My Contact Information</h2>		<div id="email"><span class="title">Email Address ::</span>  <span class="privatevalue">private</span></div>		<div id="pm">		<span class="title">My Inbox ::</span> 						<span class="value"><a href="" title="Send a message using the ezboard inbox feature" >Send me a Message!</a></span>				</div>		<div id="im"><span class="title">IM ::</span> <span class="value">None - </span></div>		<div id="link"><span class="title">Personal Link ::</span> <span class="value"><a href="" target="_blank">My Personal Link</a></span></div>		<div id="recentposts"><span class="title">Recent Posts ::</span> 										<span class="value">		<dl>				<dt><a href="http://pub147.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showMessage?topicID=42475.topic&index=74" title="post" target="_blank">Re: Casters are group dependant???</a></dt>		<dd><em>from <a href="http://pub147.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1" title="forum the above post is in" target="_blank">General</a></em></dd>				<dt><a href="http://pub147.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showMessage?topicID=42485.topic&index=22" title="post" target="_blank">Re: How does your guild handle dual-boxers and loot? </a></dt>		<dd><em>from <a href="http://pub147.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1" title="forum the above post is in" target="_blank">General</a></em></dd>				<dt><a href="http://pub147.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showMessage?topicID=42463.topic&index=83" title="post" target="_blank">Re: Questions for the dev chat</a></dt>		<dd><em>from <a href="http://pub147.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1" title="forum the above po